list.name: Default
list.comment: Fixes in Agents regarding simulation and the dashboard report. Now the simulator is fully functional, jobs and nodes are inserted to the simulation and reported in the dashboard. The jobs added runs in the mobile nodes which in turn update its intern features to report its new state after download and/or execute a job.

task.summary: Mobile Grid Simulator first commit. Added project structure and initial version of classes: - Agents - Behaviors - States This project requires the BESA library, used to develop multiagent systems.

Added new agents types Added new guards to process agents behaviors related with simulations states in the mobile node. All agents are integrated into the main class. TODO The simulator now runs but it's not showing properly the state of the jobs and/or mobile nodes.
